original_title: John Farnham: Chain Reaction - Live in Concert
overview: Recorded live over two nights during Farnham’s sellout Australian concert tour, Chain Reaction Live In Concert features all the hits from Chain Reaction, 1990’s highest selling Australian album, as well as from Farnham’s previous albums Whispering Jack and Age of Reason.
title: John Farnham: Chain Reaction - Live in Concert
